## Project Structure

```
src/
├── components/
│   ├── Login.tsx              # Login page component with modern UI
│   ├── Signup.tsx             # Signup page component with validation
│   ├── Landing.tsx            # Dashboard landing page with navigation
│   ├── ExpenseInput.tsx       # Expense input form with categories
│   ├── Summary.tsx            # Expense summary and reports
│   ├── CurrencySelector.tsx   # Currency selection component
│   ├── ErrorBoundary.tsx      # Error boundary for graceful error handling
│   ├── Loading.tsx            # Loading component
│   └── Toast.tsx              # Toast notification component
├── contexts/
│   └── ToastContext.tsx       # Toast notification context
├── types/
│   └── index.ts               # TypeScript type definitions
├── utils/
│   └── currencyUtils.ts       # Currency utility functions
├── App.tsx                    # Main app component with routing
├── App.css                    # App-specific styles
├── index.tsx                  # Application entry point
├── index.css                  # Global styles
└── theme.css                  # Theme-specific styles
